game.name: Motorbike Traffic
game.description:
Are you the biggest fan of bike driving games? You have absolutely reached at the place where you will have lots of things to do you can expect to enjoy in a typical bike racing game. Join Motorbike Traffic and allow yourself to drive your favorite motorbike at your favorite place! This brand new racing game features four maps and eight types of car models to select from. It will be amazing to drive your bike in the crowded streets of a wonderful city. Many sky-rocketing buildings are everywhere. 
You have got your bike and decided to take it and wander through crowded streets without the permission of your mom. Take your bike and select if you enjoy riding in one-way traffic or the environment of two-way traffic will give you the much needed adrenaline! No matter which option you want go with, one thing is sure that you will have great fun and thrill in a short time in this cool html5 motorbike driving game. 
Keep the graphics low, medium or high as per your wish! Select the bike model and then click the Next button to move forward! Make sure you have selected the stage between One Way, Two Way, Time Attack and Speed Bomb before diving into enter the amazing 3D racing challenge. You also have to select the stage later between Sunny and Night mode. Once you crash with other vehicle, you will lose your game and the screen will display you some information about total distance you have covered, near miss, keep above 100/H and how many vehicles you pass in opposite direction. All the best to access more car speed games on atmegame.com for free, with no install required!
